        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Windows 清除 DNS 缓存命令</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清空 dns</span></span><br><span class="line">$ ipconfig /flushdns</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看 dns</span></span><br><span class="line">$ ipconfig /displaydns</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
